name\":\"林阿國\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112217170453117439234/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBs3h_lDP7HIwqaEe93AZ3RIssRPO5mnw3QS2gWhbTp72eqIwV=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"老字號餐廳\\n主打義大利麵焗烤飯麵\\n跟幾款定食\\n\\n套餐有附濃湯跟飲料\\n這次點了奶油雞肉義大利麵\\n麵都是筆管麵\\n吃不習慣的要注意\\n焗烤點了馬鈴薯泥\\n可以說是澱粉炸彈\\n飽足感非常重\\n\\n不失為午餐晚餐好選擇\",\"time\":1746234484,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Po\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100733659404939869224/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIQ3itmoBWj-GdInS0Ft39JdFSinmiB190H1PLaZzcqmWtLhWW=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 個月前\",\"text\":\"適合家庭來這裡吃，在下巷中，推薦焗烤系列\",\"time\":1743921319,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"趴趴亂走 的狐狸\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118388211259202782644/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZ0N_hGmvJl863WYKqXcMmqRZHyzEumYedlzC-WAd6Eyom9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"9 個月前\",\"text\":\"剛出社會曾來過一兩次，之後好久沒再來過。覺得是個學生或初出茅廬打牙祭的好地方。很colorful 的名稱與裝潢，快20年了，與記憶相比有點老舊了。\\n但焗烤依然很懷念，很多選擇，主食還可以麵，飯或芋泥三選二的搭配。義大利麵是通心粉不是麵條。整個口感及肉質很順，沒有太鹹或是花草香料來混淆。\\n紅茶有幾種選擇。我選了羅漢果紅茶... 完全沒感受到紅茶而是羅漢果味道佔據。不會太甜，還不錯。\",\"time\":1725803492,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"劉陳怡君\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102919309769263917840/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS8Axby4hQUlZzD1sbWU1QO5nbWQTg-orsOhQnrLftzZ-f1w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"高中畢業後常和同學來，是愛店之一～\\n\\n在當年很少餐廳會有一半洋芋一半麵（或飯）的選項，即使是20多年後的現在也依舊不多。\\n洋芋豪好吃～\\n今天吃焗烤羅勒牛，醬汁都有巴在麵上，非常入味😋😋😋\\n起司和當年一樣給得很大氣，讚👍👍\\n\\n今天是滿滿回憶的一餐，跟記憶中一樣好吃😋\",\"time\":1699108236,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Liz Tien\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109285781874994716490/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpZrxbD_rsQd42CVJhimFXKv-L6fm6Wg1PKpKO77TXxBSbzWk2Og=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"焗烤洋芋系列\\n非常好吃美味\\n店內用餐環境\\n非常寬敞舒適\\n老闆親切有禮\\n每次都會想一來再來👍👍👍👍👍\",\"time\":1746180162,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNSwcFU-ULL12U-SaKBTwCaJPYSVpmllUuC1N0xAer2JmkHSkFbcj83AVbPqWk2mY0s9nvbE5dd6wdVHHrhLNtO11l6uVq6n2Twf__1qswss5tf3NZ7OM1Q6auSMpNgvni_exfVrBsQCWnKoX10yOomVE-n4LOjmSCwBlkC0Mz5Y7TYqcVnNG3bzagAIJUP9zas4FzGYWc1IGmGbis2v-RsLgEdAreL5DyNR-QQK8mtn-R0prG_gRBXGd8UFDqtW8OOah4G-3s7iVcJ092vuHLnA5FDUqA0qsTHE558vXhZf0p6l4HKRj3ssjMGqOBT7x1bg471OdpA\",\"AXQCQNRp_K8IhA5FzQrmglDHFj2tyuV3A9xyQX6io8OhkQTzI3tA_5eD0nd2YLCgY2o4BpRhGH7T4a8C65yyx8lplUBGma9CcbjWgot01vruWxzfsbijl7cqGj-xxQXzrz2U7Sdz_ps3VrUMcbFAVHODHXIsMZjYuoYeNaqYPuLCtpCBYgYkx0etIMS7XVPQtZvycmBBNzbr51xwCjPotOigYBJDzOOKeQ6XMQiZmQFUPzSSXotT9mVHflaVAxYRKL55nO3UbsxrSjTPyrwIh0dskEN3V0Obqszd6YETLy4a3ym7u_4IUMibHkisqfwMfs29izAIYgPKwGs\",\"AXQCQNQKF_AOgXlpcF0Y0eizbmP2DTIaMdObzZpJPqx-C2q0TIQfTKnSsfkTldWTHrRpjIzEySC_tRPGW-5B60c3JYEliU_t3jvuCh8Ah-JJ4ZBbJ6yOAkwIVplexneKUjLselcnQEox4BLdLxE15F5I-Da3UGAGqmes28Mx_6xqrv5kfhKR6BMB0W32u4X6X_RLtfmMWjW3xpvqPTADToLQDUh1tIuDYUKUKU5rcAUP7mv-SNfRnTqQTBQpb4Ydzrmj-T4ekyzGBs1qY0yutDNZugErEeRXEtDxDgj9wHbhw6XXLHpR9GzTKJiaR03KVc0GGu0u-lEY_jg\",\"AXQCQNRa7Gxv9yj-GO0IFbaQdQ1JdI6nFN4ivbkJBCLO3Qd81enDEa4NhCXLJl5CkF35QVB7Ti3KPtitHZyQpZtDbE_xSU6OwKquLD3TgjK1jHRUmOUEyKwahtc2QoP3DmA2I-mZ0iSV2m0m9eW39KAW2dCs1Gfqf6q0Jk1TNdpOkML4xy4qvHK1MkwjHQ8Za_lLqjRmlgc1IZk91Z9pXnJ4iLxWo7z1YG44TJO8YYhanO1R9b-yaRsWsCgphZlX36VH6S5ktul_KQPx9Kscae3FoLM2lOJjxVpuYyRhZ4tQao3OmNPCpCRCyF3xtc_xDX7xu9zV4uXoBIVePbzFzsmhEImsRRmPOsJjBwuTAdeA-ep19tMAQQ7oemELUEAFUvwri_CR_UmEJVOEpW2fMwuhLIByR5Slk8vxOaewrBjVTUK_izx6BDvSmok-O1FwXAap8zJaK