ww.google.com/maps/contrib/115332155293107573806/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSqa3aOe70L7QK-EcV8ZiR1ZKn2mDsnDQwfijFGcyOlX4sJXY6Rg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 個月前\",\"text\":\"炸豬排內部多汁，配不配醬汁都是不錯，另有高麗菜絲可搭胡麻醬或和風醬都十分爽口還有醃蘿蔔泡菜跟黑豆及百香果醃木瓜開胃，整體吃起來舒服。\",\"time\":1739753864,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"SAIYA WANG\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105765670686342985840/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvcIjvAVD-cMVh9uCiTD-etiF733sH3iivEAmqJrTkQI73yrk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"2025/04/21\\n新竹很棒的炸豬排店\\n食物風味跟之前去感覺有所變化\\n小菜口味不太一樣？\\n（不確定是太長時間沒吃還是個人口味有改變）\\n\\n腰內肉質嫩\\n整體口味不會偏膩\\n但本次的蘿蔔泥搭配\\n好像汁水太多\\n吃到後面豬底部的麵衣已經變軟爛\\n（進食速度中等，不會到很慢）\\n\\n高麗菜絲可以一直續\\n店員服務也很棒\\n平日可以跟朋友聊天沒有用餐時間限制\\n會一直續茶\\n服務費10%，可以現金&刷卡\\n\\n依然是新竹可以被期待的食物\",\"time\":1745556749,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Chieh Wu\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108522594849868586625/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpT9s-IG-G8ZPg2UZOodKXYYR0MYwflAAnrzRyASIwUGfzx5Yg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"5 個月前\",\"text\":\"從之前在護城河邊到現在的位置，一直覺得是新竹最好吃的炸豬排 入口超酥😋連附餐都很精緻～高麗菜絲 米飯 跟小菜都很優秀\",\"time\":1734179090,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"jojo lu\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118144320977726983059/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPDhjAV3RVY8ldcOIFYXvCyZTmLk9jGkyIWmfptX0fyXyPG5k=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"9 個月前\",\"text\":\"小菜給的很大方，可以無限自取\\n黑豆很好吃～\\n\\n我主餐點的是里肌豬排，\\n炸得酥脆，肉嫩又有口感給讚\\n\\n魷魚選的好\\n\\n玉子燒有點失望，上面的美乃滋油耗味很重\\n跟玉子燒很不搭\\n\\n起司可樂餅表現一般般，是好吃的\",\"time\":1725202267,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Ching\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102416367609103309278/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSwWy-VHBAtBno--HTWbuqGmGbrjmSnxcsUcYoETz3hI2Fzn8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"🔹浦燒鰻魚定食套餐 $600\\n🔹明太子腰內豬排套餐 $450\\n\\n套餐的米飯（越光米）、醬菜（黑豆、香橙蘿蔔、韓式泡菜、百香青木瓜、辣蘿蔔）、高麗菜絲皆可續加‼️\\n\\n鰻魚飯使用一整隻肉質鮮甜的鰻魚，搭配特調醬汁，香甜爽口，烤的好下飯，好吃 🤤🤤\\n\\n炸豬排是帶有些許油脂口感的腰內肉，加上炸的酥脆的麵衣，再加上微甜卡滋卡滋的明太子，好吃好吃啊 🧡💚💜\\n\\n還有提供熱茶，服務人員很用心，會一直詢桌詢問是否加茶和醬菜，我特愛百香青木瓜，套餐的味噌湯也是料多實在，一直都是我很喜歡的店家 💕\\n\\n歡迎關注我的IG：hsinchu_foodfood\",\"time\":1711920431,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNTYKXqWOA965fULk7Dyj6MJa5Kwis2V-1jhSL2-ARGTXZimCBkwvgPw_Uhb2aEDAU-mFGuDVUZw0e1inR8EuoSLGNULsuSysCPS5SNXX94zahChgfPcSi1GLtRT4ButjEIxpQanPy8IADHvxVhzJi6PAJsmu9NwHuXfTeeGX2EKFcnvVS_EEuzA4ooTZ1Lr4gvT9Z1ZXLBfiOVg76onJK_E0BvE4_bgR17UkN7rT9PMEC7-WeZJFX4JVRxHxxB9d7OTgoLL-QppT505Jj3KSbI3Ojzj01xvSy0NBLVKjuh2sy6JKCQOiNvTwggZPvCN2-kbyCFyuB0\",\"AXQCQNS45UAqMzOyUsKQiqFuIvlIjbbsfKdt6dX1CLqUZpVu78KUwVPxY132nOFadhwjjUq7eAVqqaf2j2CbLJPDQjR_bLksHzU03MwbGWf674YXV8C03jKJkL7eLYzlRY_mOV5LHR-dZnh7Lyig_W9GB7YIbZJuhcp_vzzmfjEFfKFC2e3rLd4jE2Bnj0K6Bnz_7fDwgpouyZXi-IkzfOUsujHmvyr4w87QUCFMFZ27o5AdUorn7-YiWNHuUl84NX0gXkVkpdh1rqbFRDWqhr1pGfRKp5aTuinLGlb9qVayctmsebMNXqqXffdA3i2zkbW6IbVhRuogUk0\",\"AXQCQNTmHyTzqCkNFqSr47-hk521k-l6WWVDpF3gukT3KgSWtb_Qx5II4l4fmXWOZTU58wTHkiIom-Y97KPKsu30aZDyGgybsTeTuDp0EeH3ZAQ8ZRusGjpvC3AWsqDj5ime40I-VHAarF-6yVR3Blwoko2NztBGbESSj_bsgicrI3pj9Ce0yTQpyjKoUwk_KH_S9LL3KhfbX1UTUyvCc1vE0ehCK3Pn7CUQL2iHJnrtFyh-Qcrev6kT0VZtbxrS8ye4348qG-TunHXZGxhdnZHTZdvgPXMAcY7NQw_Jfiw2OSrL9wdCgjMi-igi9BPQnhdIAFLv8Q_mr2U\",\"AXQCQNTISHauNWqg851NsYHlRls4PqXavg36mklNKrj_9EzJ7hYkrdtQOeGT3HEERVY5Hs__gFcEYPNLHIeMmdQ9URO3JdWAw4Oa81FsvanVJLzoS3hpcLperr_pwJQDJSnLxH_8Hy8xfd40D-WP6Vkkjy36m6Ap2SxwHiwpBK6V4pwFiKulgZyxYdGpC0BfGM4ln8XAJZ8qIHg6trR6SWE9Q6xSp05931RmE5xL29pjeWlBzj74mFb1ukDP